text.tspan: Share of people with at least one dose of COVID-19 vaccine by age,
Share of the population in each age group that has received at least one vaccine dose. This may not equal the share that has
completed the initial protocol if the vaccine requires two doses.
Note: In some territories, vaccination coverage may include non-residents (such as tourists and foreign
workers) so per-capita metrics may exceed 100%.
Data source: Official data collated by Our World in Data
